# No tool or assistant attribution

Never add signatures, footers, badges, or bylines that credit Cursor, ChatGPT, Copilot, Claude, or
any other assistant or AI tool - in commits, code, comments, MDX, README, PR descriptions, issue
text, or config. The full rule (with examples) lives under **Code Style** in `AGENTS.md`, the
canonical rulebook. This file keeps the rule `alwaysApply` for Cursor.
